org.apache.flink.runtime.webmonitor

类 StackTraceSample

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.webmonitor.StackTraceSample

  • public class StackTraceSample
extends Object
    A sample of stack traces for one or more tasks.

    The sampling is triggered in StackTraceSampleCoordinator.

        public StackTraceSample(int sampleId,
                        long startTime,
                        long endTime,
                        Map<org.apache.flink.runtime.executiongraph.ExecutionAttemptID,List<StackTraceElement[]>> stackTracesByTask)
        Creates a stack trace sample
        参数:
        sampleId - ID of the sample.
        startTime - Time stamp, when the sample was triggered.
        endTime - Time stamp, when all stack traces were collected at the JobManager.
        stackTracesByTask - Map of stack traces by execution ID.
